data.description: Excellent Warren ranch set on a large lot.  This comfortable home offers 2 bedrooms, 1 bathroom and roomy living spaces.  The large deck off the back overlooks the yard with mature plantings and trees.  A huge detached garage offers endless opportunities and uses.  New roof in 2019.
